Flesh out Brainrot City: more skyline, lampposts, lit path to the arena

The plaza read a bit empty, so: four more parody towers on the open side/front
edges (Meme Mobile, Neon Cola, The Goblet, Rizz Fuel), a ring of neon lampposts
around the perimeter, and a lit path leading from the spawn up to the arena.

